{"tid":2002107,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邊境爆炸案手足: 你若不離開， 我定不放棄！","createTime":"2020-05-05T04:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T17:47:54.000Z","uid":134071,"like":123,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"351c44e2c95ccb1597d17d5cc39dc52dfb04a60d","tid":2002107,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:16:15.000Z","msg":"唔好意思.<br />\n手足信要貼哂.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200505/BTLKYFLCVEA7MQ7RDYBII63E6A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200505%2FBTLKYFLCVEA7MQ7RDYBII63E6A%2F&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktX%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=7a640177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200505%2FBTLKYFLCVEA7MQ7RDYBII63E6A%2F&h=866c0dca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200505/BTLKYFLCVEA7MQ7RDYBII63E6A/</a><br />\n<br />\n致各位同路人︰<br />\n大家好，我是其中一位捲入邊境爆炸案的手足，就是被探員在警署黑布幪頭、打了數分鐘，現在左眼失去部份視力那位。<br />\n今天是4月8日，我永遠忘不了一個月前那天，在和女友相約共度良宵的晚上，會和家人及深愛的人相隔一段長時間，會被五名探員黑布幪頭暴打數分鐘，會被腳踢心口兩次，會被腳踏下體兩次，會被大力把頭撞到枱面一次，左面額頭會被大力拳打兩次，結果導致左眼失去三成視野角度，看到光源會頭痛，偶然會失焦。這些一般人不會想像到的暴力對待，是可以突然降臨到你身上，當你住在一個充滿警暴的城市。<br />\n大家可能會問我感受如何，當然是很傷心，很憤怒，但其實比起被射爆眼睛的女FA和印尼女記者，我受的痛和傷算得上甚麼？還有被打到掉牙的小兄弟，中槍的健仔和熊仔餅，7.21被打到頭破血流的路人，每一個都比我承受更大的痛苦！<br />\n我最大的希望是，請你們不要忘記我們每一個流的血、受的傷，好嗎？五大訴求，我們爭取到了多少？請記着我們受的傷，我們失去的自由、親情和愛情，只要你們不放棄，我們在鐵籠中也會堅持下去。<br />\n<strong>你若不離（開），<br />\n我定不（放）棄！</strong><br />\nSNAKE<br />\n2020年4月8日<br />\n<br />\n<strong>（編按：此為工黨立法會議員張超雄收到被還柙手足的公開信，由張超雄代為投稿。如有意回信，請寄到「中區立法會道一號立法會綜合大樓1017室張超雄立法會議員辦事處」，註明回覆給哪位手足，以及留低電話號碼或其他聯絡方法，方便議辦跟進。）</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200504/large/1588604435_b437.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200504%2Flarge%2F1588604435_b437.jpg&h=342857ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f95d59683c1f3a9d8b29799d75ce850a9fd024a0","tid":2002107,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac76b3bebf44dacc8949729058ffee397a337e3","tid":2002107,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c4c32c5c0f6bd6ac3acfa0c19345f5d572aa9c","tid":2002107,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd9aab35c11929af939627193280eca7d8c25d4","tid":2002107,"uid":16844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:17:08.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人唔好放棄"},{"pid":"184ce9e47089f5e6d4ae85fd93b0501ea03c76c1","tid":2002107,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f1f1fb77baeedde1f31803d0efe6abc2e7edd5","tid":2002107,"uid":3705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fe34cc1efa52e542ed1afc8bc54d35e017f93c","tid":2002107,"uid":167567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"199295d3ac8d1606cee604199f6f639403bc3725","tid":2002107,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a22bb7fdfeed4d6e19a4289a9041cd9691b218","tid":2002107,"uid":204872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\